content.rendered:
Directed by Hadi Abrar.

Written by M. Salim.

Cast Ronit Roy(Mansoor Ali). Ashmit Patel(Siddhant Prabhu). Gashmeer Mahajani(Raja). Reecha Sinha(Shruti Waghmare / Prabhu) .Muntazir Ahmad. Ashwini Kalsekar(Rukhsar – Raja’s foster mother). Farhan Rehman Khan((Kashif)). Harshad Kumar(Constable).Madhur Kumar. Sanjeev Kumar(Younger brother). Sunny Leone(Dancer). Kumar Saurabh(Goonga). Kamlesh Sawant(Damle). Sacheen Suvarna(Daya). Mukesh Tiwari(Qawwali singer)

Language Hindi.

Producers Ps Chhatwal. Sameer Mahabale. Satish Mane. Ravi Singh. Ravi Singh.

Production Filmy Keeda Production.
